  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency bundlesize to v0.15.3",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/siddharthkp/bundlesize\">bundlesize</a> from <code>v0.15.2</code> to <code>v0.15.3</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>siddharthkp/bundlesize</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"0153\">0.15.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/siddharthkp/bundlesize/commit/f6aa6e9a243023c942500db16735b920ea43f2d4\"><code>f6aa6e9</code></a> 0.15.3</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/siddharthkp/bundlesize/commit/e0527bd56b7c88a1b424afee16ab99d275295bcf\"><code>e0527bd</code></a> Remove opencollective postinstall</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/siddharthkp/bundlesize/commit/7efbcd50192480e15edbf857399bdd9890ec0520\"><code>7efbcd5</code></a> remove backers, put sponsors on top</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/siddharthkp/bundlesize/commit/3892f1a732304513e622a7500263d3750f5db98a\"><code>3892f1a</code></a> Add quotes to cli example</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/siddharthkp/bundlesize/commit/7eaca5fde7db60b435fcdc2566d2a1e0e74bf7e3\"><code>7eaca5f</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;163 from XhmikosR/patch-1</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/siddharthkp/bundlesize/commit/0ab8fac401ed6b2d8fb4096693515598c59027ee\"><code>0ab8fac</code></a> Update README.md</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/siddharthkp/bundlesize/commit/ea90e2ee2e2a4e63541a2558e9f6e5c0da9b2130\"><code>ea90e2e</code></a> Add bootstrap to users (#&#8203;160)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/siddharthkp/bundlesize/commit/2e53726177ee141b1341a8de39f6bf22b077f107\"><code>2e53726</code></a> Add totally tooling tips link :)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/siddharthkp/bundlesize/commit/03aa4bf0efd170cec69b925d93f6c3d4f7286760\"><code>03aa4bf</code></a> Add size-limit to similar projects</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/siddharthkp/bundlesize/commit/1e302b49989447be6068b028d368e77dfbde82b4\"><code>1e302b4</code></a> fix build (#&#8203;153)</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
